 c_n = \frac{4^n a^n ~ U(-n,1/2,b^2/4a)}{(2n)!} \sim \frac{\sqrt{2}}{4 n}\left(\frac{ea}{n^{3/2}}\right)^n c'_{even}(a,b)~~~~\text{ ( n even )}
